quran[126]{c,v,t}:
  2,253,"ЖҒen NulaaЙ“e, Men ЖҒurnii yoga maЙ“Й“e e dow yoga : No e maЙ“Й“e yeewtiduЙ“e e Alla, O ЖҒaЕӢti darjaaji yoga e maЙ“Й“e; Men Rokki Iisaa, Й“iЙ—Й—o Maryama on, Й“anngannduyeeji Men semmbiniri mo fittaandu laaЙ“undu ndun. Si Alla Muuyuno, womЙ“e Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e Й“en wartindirtaano Й“aawo nde Й“anngannduyeeji Й—in ari maabЙ“e. Kono Й“e luutondiri: no e maЙ“Й“e Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e, no e maЙ“Й“e Й“en yedduЙ“e. Si Alla Muuyuno, Й“e wartindirtaano, kono Alla no waЙ—a kon ko O YiЙ—i"
  2,254,"Ko onon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e, sakkee e kon ko Men Arsiki on adii Гұalaande arde; nde ngeyngu alaa e mayre, wanaa sehilaaku, wanaa tefoore. Ko heeferЙ“e Й“en woni tooГұooЙ“e Й“en"
  2,255,"Alla, alaa reweteezo si wanaa kanko, WuurЙ—o Г‘iiЙ“uЙ—o. ЕҠoЕӢre nanngataa Mo, wanaa kadi Й—oyngol. ko Kanko Jeyi huunde ko woni ka kammuuli e huunde ko woni ka leydi. Ko hommbo woni on tefoowo ka Makko si wanaa e duЕӢayee Makko? Himo anndi ko woni yeeso maЙ“Й“e, e ko woni Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e. ЖҒe huЙ“indotaako huunde e Anndal Makko ngal si wanaa ko O Muuyi. Jullere Makko nden no yaaji Й“uri kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin. Reenugol Й—i aaninaa Mo. Ko Kano woni ToowuЙ—o MawЙ—o On. @Corrected"
  2,256,"Doolugol alaa ka diina. GomЙ—ii peewal ngal Й“anngii immorde e majjere nden. Kala yedduЙ—o Й—uuЙ—a bewreeru ndun o gomЙ—ini Alla, haray o jogitike Й“oggi finnde hoolaare Й—in, firtagol alanaa Й—i. Alla ko Nanoowo AnnduЙ—o"
  2,257,"Alla Ko GiЙ—o gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en: Himo yaltina Й“e e niЙ“e, O naЙ“a Й“e e ndaygu. ЖҒeya yedduЙ“e, yiЙ—Й“e maЙ“Й“e ko Й—uuЙ—a bewreeji Й—in: HiЙ—i yaltina Й“e e ndaygu naЙ“a Й“e e niЙ“e. ЖҒen ko yimЙ“e yiite, luttooЙ“e e magge"
  2,258,"E a yi'aali on wennjuЙ—o Ibraahiima e fii JeyЙ—o mo On, fii Alla no YeЙ—i mo laamu, nde Ibraahiima maakunoo: \"JeyЙ—o lam on, ko On Wuurnata Wara\". [WennjuЙ—o on] wi'i: \"Min kadi miЙ—o wuurna wara\". Ibraahiima maaki: \"Pellet Alla no Addira naange ngen fuЙ—naange, addir nge hiirnaange\".YedduЙ—o on mugaa. Alla fewnataa yimЙ“e tooГұooЙ“e Й“en"
  2,259,"Wolla ko hono oon birtiiЙ—o wuro yeewngo ngo maadi mum e mbildi mum yirbi o wi*i hono Alla wuurtaninta Й—um caggal maayde mum? Alla wari mbo o lelii duuЙ“i teemedere O ummini mbo O daali hono foti ГұiiЙ“Й—a o wi*i Гұalawma maa feccere Гұalawma, O daali alah a duumiima Й—o duuЙ“i teemedere Жҙeew Гұaamdu ma e njaram ma waylaaki ndaaru mbabba ma ba, ngam min mbaЙ— ma maande wonande yimЙ“e, Жҙeew Жҙi*e nomin cardataЙ—e refti Min muurdaЙ—e teew, nde Й—uum feeГұi mbo o wi*i mi anndi Alla na hattani kala huundeЙ“Й—ЖҙЖҙГұj"
  2,260,"Nde Ibraahiima maaki joom am hollam na nguurtanirta maayЙ“e, O daali mate a goonЙ—inaani? o maaki ohonkay kono ko haa Й“ernde am deeЖҙa , O daali nanngu colli nay tappuЙ—i faade e ma refti mbaЙ—a e kala tulde feccere e colli he refti nodduЙ—i Й—i ngara e ma hoЙ—i njaha anndu Alla ko pooloowo mbo fooletaake ko O ГұeeГұo"
  2,261,Yeru Й“een nafkooЙ“e e laawol Alla ko honbbere fuЙ—nunde butaali njeeЙ—iЙ—i in wutaandu fof teemedere abbere Alla na sowana Mo O welaa Alla ko jaacЙ—o Ganndo
  2,262,NafkooЙ“e jawdi mum en e laawol Alla refti Й“e ndewnatah e koЙ“e ko wacde wolla lor woodaniiЙ“e njobdi mum en ka joomi mum en kulol alanaaЙ“e Й“e ngonah sunotooЙ“e
  2,263,"Konngol lobbol Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude e sadaka dewnateeЙ—o lorla, Alla ko Gala yondaniiЙ—o munyoowo"
  2,264,"Eehey mon goonЙ—inЙ“e wotee mbonniree sadakuuji mon wacde e lorlude hono oon tottirЙ—o jawdi mum yeenga yimЙ“e o goonЙ—inaani Alla e Гұalngu cakkatiingu o wayi kono haaЖҙre Й—aatnde toЙ“o yani e mayre acci nde honde wa*i e teeleende Й“een kattantah hay huunde e ko Й“e paggatii ko,Alla feewnatah yimЙ“e heefereeЙ“e Й“e"
  2,265,"Yeru Й“een nafkooЙ“e jawdi mum en ngam Й—aЙ“Й“ude welu Alla e tabatinde pittaali mum en ko hono ngesa ngonba e dow tulde toЙ“o heewngo heewngo yani e heba ba, ba addi cowe Й—iЙ“Й—e ko ba addatno si ba toЙ“aam Гұuur Гұuur koba hecca mbelba balangol A na yi*a ko mbaЙ—aton ko"
  2,266,"Mbela gooto e mon na yiЙ—i nde o daГұata ngesa tamaro e inabeeje na ila e les mabba caatli te homba jogii e heba kala Й“eynaaЙ—e, o naywi hombo jogii Й“eyngu loongu henndu wondundu e yiite yana e ngesa he ba suma, ko hona nih Min Й“annganirta kaawisaaji Й—i mbela miictaЙ—on"
  2,267,"Eehey mon goonЙ—inЙ“e tottiree ko laaЙ“i ummaade ko paggiti Й—on e ko Min njaltinani on ka leydi, wotee paande ko soЙ“i ko ngam nafkude heen on ngonah nanngooЙ“e Й—um si wonah on meerni heen, ngannde Alla ko yondaniiЙ—o MantaaЙ—o"
  2,268,"Seytaane na fodana on baasal o yamira on pankare, Alla noon na fodana on yaafuya ummaade e Makko e Й“ural Alla ko jaacЙ—o ko O Ganndo"
  2,269,"Hombo totta ГұeeГұal mbo O wela kala tottaaЙ—o ГұeeГұal o tottaa ma moЖҙЖҙere mawnde, siftortah Й—um si wonah joman hakkiillaaji"
  2,270,"Kala ko tottirЙ—on e nafake wolla takkuЙ—on e takkere pellet Alla na anndi Й—uum, woodanaani tooГұooЙ“e wallooЙ“e"
  2,271,Si on Й“annginii sadakeeji na ЖҙЖҙi si on cuuЙ—i Й—i tottuЙ—on Й—i waasЙ“e ko Й—uum Й“uri on moЖҙЖҙande O hafrana on bonЙ—i mon Alla na humpitii ko golloton ko
  2,272,"A fawaaki peewal mum en kono ko Alla feewnata mbo O faala, kala ko tottirЙ—on e moЖҙЖҙere ko ko*e mon woodani on nafkatah si wonah ngam Alla kala ko tottirЙ—on e moЖҙЖҙere tottite Й—um e mbaadi timmundi onon de on tooГұetaake"
  2,273,"Woodanii waasЙ“e suraaЙ“e gaa e laawol Alla Й“e mbaawah yaade e leydi hee, majjuЙ“e na cikka koЙ“e alЙ—uЙ“e sabu Й—uurnaade aduna ana anndiraЙ“e maandeeji mum en Й“e Гұaagataaka yimЙ“e e mbaadi cattundi kala ko tottirЙ—on Alla na anndi Й—um"
  2,274,"TootirooЙ“e jawdi mum en jemma e Гұalawma e mbaadi mbirniindi e mbaadi Й“anngundi, Й“een de woodaniiЙ“e njbdi mum en ummaade ka joomi mum en kulol woodanaani Й“e Й“e ngonah sunatooЙ“e"
  2,275,"Й“een ГұaamooЙ“e riba Й“e ummataako si wonah no mbo seytaani memi Й—uum noon ko sabu wiide Й“e pellet njeegu wa*i kono riba, Alla noon daknii njeeygu O harmini riba, kala mbo waaju ummmarii mbo ka Alla o acci woodanii mbo o Й“enni ko fiyaaku makko e Alla fawii, kala duttiiЙ—o noon ko Й“een ngoni joman en yiite saasooЙ“e e henge haa pooma"
  2,276,Alla na momto riba na Й“amta sadakuuji Alla yiЙ—ah kala keeЙ—o keefeeru e bakkadinoowo sanne
  2,277,Й“een goonЙ—inЙ“e ngolli ko moЖҙЖҙi o darni juulde o tottiri askal woodaniiЙ“e jobdi mum en ummaade ko joomi mum en kulol alanaaЙ“e Й“e ngonah sunatooЙ“e
  2,278,Eehey mon goonЙ—inЙ“e kulee Alla accon ko heddii ko e riba si on ngonii goonЙ—uЙ“e
  2,279,Si on mbaЙ—aani Й—uum kolliree hare ummorde e Alla e nelaaЙ—o MakkoJJJЙ“J
  2,280,"Si tawii o wonii e satteende yo o muГұane haa e yaajeende,nde cakkorton Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude e mon si on ngonii annduЙ“e"
  2,281,Kulee Гұalngu ngu ndutteteЙ—on ka Alla refti yoЙ“ee kala fittaandu ko ndu faggitii ko kamЙ“e Й“e tooГұetaake
  2,282,"Eehey mon goonЙ—inЙ“e si on Гұamlandiri nyamaande faade happu dottaaЙ—o mbinndee nde, yo nuunЙ—uЙ—o winndu hakkunde mon, woto binndoowo sala winndude yo o winndu no Alla anndiniri mbo, yo o winndu yo mbo hakke woni dow mum winndu yo o hul joomiiko woto o ustu heen hay huunde, si wonii mbo hakke woni e dow mum ko Й—aayЙ—o wolla lohЙ—o wollo o waawah fidde, yo keedo makko fidir nuunЙ—al, ceednee seede en Й—iЙ—o e worЙ“e mon, si worЙ“e Й—iЙ—o ngalah ko gorko e rewЙ“e Й—iЙ—o Й“e mbelete Й—on e seedeeli ngam si gooto e maЙ“Й“e yrdditi goЙ—Й—o o siftirina mbo, woto seedeeli cala siЙ“e noddaama, wote kaaste winndude ko famЙ—i maa ko heewi faade e happu mum, ko Й—uum Й“uri nuunЙ—ude ka Alla Й“uri fooccaade wonande seede Й“uri kadi Й“adaade waasde mon sikkitaade, si wonah kommersaagu ngonaangu ngu yiilaton hakkunde mon, ndeen noon bakkaat alah e mon nde mbaasaton Й—um winndude, ceetnee si on yeeyandiri woto binndoowo e seede lore, si on waЙ—ii Й—uum pellet Й—uum ko faasikaagal e mon, kulee Alla O anndina on Alla ko kattanЙ—o kala huunde"
  2,283,"Si on ngonii e Й—atngal on keЙ“aani binndoowo tottirre jukunnde tamaande, si on koolandirii, oon tottaaЙ—o hoolaare yo tottit hoolaare nde, yo o hul Alla joom makko, wotee cuuЙ—e seedanfaagu kala cuuЙ—o ngu pellet oon Й“ernde makko ko bakkadinnde, Alla na anndi ko ngollaton ko"
  2,284,"Woodanii Alla ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi si on Й“annginii ko e pittaali mon wolla on cuuЙ—i ma Alla haasbu mon sabu mum, O yaafoo mbo O wela O lepta mbo wela, Alla ko kattanЙ—o kala huunde"
  2,285,"NulaaЙ—o goonЙ—anii ko jippinaa ko e Makko ummade e Joom Makko, e gooninЙ“e Й“e fof Й“e goonЙ—anii Alla e malaykaaji Makko e defte makko e NulaaЙ“e makko, min ceerndatah hay gooto e NulaaЙ“e makko, Й“e wii min nanii min Й—oftiima hafran amen Joomi amen ko Mah woni ruttorde"
  2,286,"Alla fawatah fittaandu kondu hattanaani,woodanii ndu kondu faggii, fawiima e dow mayru kondu faggitii,Joomi amen woto nanngir min ko min njjiti ko wollo ko min ngoopi ko,woto A faw e amen tampere hono no ndoondirnaЙ—a Й“een adiiЙ“e amen,Joomi amen woto faw min komin kattanaani,yaafa amin cuura bakkatuuJi amen nJurmaЙ—a min ko Aan woni keeda amin wollu min e dow yimЙ“e heefereeЙ“e Й“e"
  3,1,"Alif, Laam, Miim"
  3,2,"Alla: reweteeЙ—o woo alaa si wanaa KaЕӢko. Ko O WuurЙ—o, Г‘iiЙ“uЙ—o"
  3,3,"O Jippinirii Deftere nden dow maaЙ—a e goonga, goonginnde ko adii nde, O Jippini Tawreeta e Linnjiila"
  3,4,"Ko adii, fii fewnugol yimЙ“e Й“en, O Jippini AlQur'aana. Pellet yedduЙ“e Aayeeje Alla Й—en, hino woodani Й“e lepte saЙ—tuЙ—e. Alla Ko FooluЙ—o, Jom-yottagol"
  3,5,"Pellet, Alla, huunde suuЙ—otaako Mo ka leydi wanaa ka kammu"
  3,6,"Ko KaЕӢko Woni Mbaadiniroowo on ka renngaaji noone woo no O Muuyiri. ReweteeЙ—o woo alaa si wanaa KaЕӢko, FooluЙ—o, Г‘eeГұuЙ—o"
  3,7,"Ko KaЕӢko Woni JippinЙ—o Deftere nden e maaЙ—a, no e mayre aayeeje Й“aЕӢnguЙ—e; ko kaЕӢje woni neene Deftere nden, e goЙ—Й—e goo nannduЙ—e. Ammaa Й“en Й“e ooГұaare woni e nder Й“erЙ—e mun, hiЙ“e jokka ko nanndi kon e majje Й—aЙ“Й“ugol fitina e Й—aЙ“ugol firtugol Й—e. Anndataa firo majje si wanaa Alla. TutiiЙ“e Й“en e ganndal no wi'a: \"Men gomЙ—inii nde, kala mun ko immorde ka Joomi amen\". Waajitotaako si wanaa joomiraaЙ“e haqqillaaji Й“en"
  3,8,"joomi amen, wata ooГұu Й“erЙ—e amen Й—en Й“aawo nde fewnu-Й—aa men, yeЙ—u men yurmeende immorde ka MaaЙ—a.Pellet An, ko An Woni YeЙ—oowo=dokko"
  3,9,"Joomi amen, pellet An ko A MooЙ“oyoowo yimЙ“e Й“en Гұalnde nde sikke alah e mun Pellet Alla luutintaa fodoore nden"
  3,10,"Pellet Й“en yedduЙ“e, jawle maЙ“Й“e e Й“iЙ—Й“e maЙ“Й“e duncaЕӢtaaЙ“e e lepte Alla Й—en hay e huunde. Ko Й“en woni carmale yiite ngen"
  3,11,"Wano mbowdi yimЙ“e Fir'awna e Й“en adinooЙ“e Й“e. ЖҒe fennii aayeeje Amen Й—en, Alla Nanngitiri Й“e junubaaji maЙ“Й“e Й—in. Alla ko SaЙ—tuЙ—o lepte"
  3,12,"Maakan Й“en yedduЙ“e: \"On fooloyte mooЙ“oye-Й—on ka jahannama\". Nge bonii ndaЙ—Й—udi"
  3,13,"GomЙ—ii laatanike on aaya e Й—in feddeejji Й—iЙ—i fottuЙ—i fiihaЙ“ugol: fedde goo no haЙ“a e laawol Alla, wonnde goo ko yeddunde, hiЙ“e yi'iraЙ“e yeru maЙ“Й“e laawЙ“i Й—iЙ—i giiЙ—e gite. Alla no Semmbinira balla Makko ngal o Mo O Muuyi. Pellet, no e Й—um waaju wonannde joomiraaЙ“e-haqqillaaji"
  3,14,"YimЙ“e Й“en cuЙ—inanaama yiЙ—ugol tuuyooji: immorde e rewЙ“e e Й“iЙ—Й“e worЙ“e, e jawle tuginidiraaЙ—e, immorde e kaЕӢЕӢe e kaalise, e pucci ЕӢarЙ—iЙ—aaЙ—i, e neemoraaЙ—i, e remuru. ЖҠum Й—on, ko dakamme nguurdam aduna. Alla, no ka Makko moЖҙЖҙuЙ—um ruttorde"
  3,15,"Maaku: \"E yo mi humpitu on ko Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude e Й—um mon?\". No woodani Й“en huluЙ“e ka Joomi maЙ“Й“e, aljannaaji, no ila senngo ley majji, canЙ—i: ko Й“e luttooЙ“e ton, wondude e sonnaaЙ“e laЙ“Й“inaaЙ“e, e yerluyee immorde ka Alla. Alla ko ReЕӢtuЙ—o jeyaaЙ“e Й“en. @Corrected"
  3,16,"ЖҒen wi'ooЙ“e: \"Joomi amen, menen men gomЙ—inii, yawtan men junubaaji amen, daЙ—ndaa men lepte yiite"
  3,17,MuГұГұiiЙ“e Й“en e goonguЙ“e Й“en e Й—oftiiЙ“e Й“en e wiЕӢtooЙ“e=nafkoobe Й“en e insinotooЙ“e Й“en ka hoore-subaka
  3,18,"Alla Seedike wonde ReweteeЙ—o alaa si wanaa kaЕӢko, Malaa'ika en kadi, e joomiraaЙ“e ganndal Й“en, ko O DaraniiЙ—o nunЙ—al. ReweteeЙ—o alaa si wanaa KaЕӢko, On FooluЙ—o Г‘eeГұuЙ—o"
  3,19,"Pellet diina kan ka Alla, ko lislaamu. OkkaaЙ“e Defte Й“en lurraali si wanaa Й“aawo nde ganndal ngal arde Й“e; ka bewre hakkunde maЙ“Й“e. Kala yedduЙ—o aayeeje Alla Й—en, pellet Alla ko yaawuЙ—o hasboore"
  3,20,"Si Й“e wennjii ma, maaku: \"Mi jebbilanii yeeso an ngon e on jokkuЙ—o lam\". Maakanaa Й“en okkaaЙ“e Defte e humambinne en: \" E on jebbilike?\" Si Й“e jebbilike, gomЙ—ii Й“e feewii, si Й“e huccitii, enee, ko fawi maa ko yottingol. Alla ko ReЕӢtuЙ—o jeyaaЙ“e Й“en"
  3,21,"Pellet, Й“en yeddooЙ“e aayeeje Alla Й—en, Й“e wara AnnabaaЙ“e Й“en ko aldaa e goonga, Й“e wara Й“en yamirooЙ“e nunЙ—al, wewlinir Й“e lepte muusuЙ—e"
  3,22,"Ko Й“en woni Й“e golleeji mun boni Й“en ka aduna e ka laakara, Й“e alaa wallooЙ“e"
  3,23,"E a yi'aali okkaaЙ“e geЙ“al e Deftere nden, hiЙ“e noddee e Deftere Alla nden fii no nde Гұaawira hakkunde maЙ“Й“e, refti fedde goo e maЙ“Й“e huccita ko Й“e Й—uurniiЙ“e"
  3,24,"ЖҠum non, ko tawde Й“e wi'ii: \"Yiite ngen meemataa men si wanaa ГұalЙ—i limtaaЙ—i\". hodiiЙ“e e diina maЙ“Й“e kan, huunde nde Й“e fefindotonoo"
  3,25,"E ko hol no si Men MooЙ“oyiiЙ“e e Г‘alaande nde sikke alaa e mu'un, woЕӢkii kala hunnanee ko ki faggitii kon? KamЙ“e Й“e tooГұetaake"
  3,26,"Maaku: \"Yaa An LaamЙ—o JeyЙ—o laamu, HiЙ—a Okka laamu on mo MuuyuЙ—aa, HiЙ—a ЖҒoora laamu on mo MuuyuЙ—aa, HiЙ—a Teddina on mo MuuyuЙ—aa, HiЙ—a Hoyna on mo MuuyuЙ—aa. MoЖҙЖҙere nden ko e Junngo MaaЙ—a woni, pellet, An e huunde kala, ko A HaaЙ—tanЙ—o"
  3,27,"HiЙ—a Naadira jemma on nder Гұalorma on, HiЙ—a Naadira Гұalorma on nder jemma on. HiЙ—a Yaltina ko wuuri immorde e ko maayi, yaltinaa ko maayi immorde e ko wuur. HiЙ—a Arsika on mo MuuyuЙ—aa ko aldaa e hasboore"
  3,28,"Wata muumini en jogitor heeferЙ“e Й“en yiЙ—Й“e Й“e acca gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en. Kala huuwuЙ—o Й—um, o laataaki jeyraaЙ—o e diina Alla Kan hay e huunde, si wanaa nde huloton e maЙ“Й“e bone. Alla No ReЕӢtina on Hoore-Mun. Ko faade ka Alla woni ruttorde nden"
  3,29,"Maaku:Si on suuЙ—ii ko woni e Й“erЙ—e mon maa si on feГұГұin Й—um,Alla no Anndi Й—um,Himo Anndi ko woni ka kammuuli e ko woni e leydi Alla ko kattan-Й—o kala huunde"
  3,30,"Г‘alnde kala woЕӢkii tawata ko ki golli kon e moЖҙЖҙere hino Й“annaa, e huunde ko ki golle e bone, ki yeloo sinno wonayno hakkunde makki e majje dumunne woЙ—Й—uЙ—o. Alla no ReЕӢtina on Hoore Mun. Alla ko HilnotooЙ—o jeyaaЙ“e Й“en"
  3,31,"wi*u si wonii hidon yidi Alla, cukke e am, mi yidno mon Alla, O yaafo mon bakkatuuji mon, Alla ko kafroowo jumotoodo"
  3,32,"Maaku: \"ЖҠoftee Alla e NulaaЙ—o on\", si Й“e huccitii, pellet, Alla yiЙ—aa yedduЙ“e Й“en"
  3,33,"Pellet, Alla SuЙ“ike Aadama e Nuuhu e yimЙ“e Ibraahiima Й“en e yimЙ“e Imraana Й“en e hoore tagoore nden"
  3,34,Jurriiya=genyol yoga e maЙ“Й“e iwde e yoga. Alla ko Nanoowo AnnduЙ—o
  3,35,"Nde debbo Imraana on wi'unoo: \"Joomi an, min mi takkanii Ma kon woni ka nder reedu am, ko rinЙ—inaa Й—um, jaЙ“anam, pellet, An ko A Nanoowo AnnduЙ—o"
  3,36,"Nde o jibinnoo mo o wi'i: \"Min mi jibinii mo ko o deyel\", ko Alla Й“uri Anndude ko O jibini, gorko laataaki wano debbo. \"Min mi innii mo Maryama, min mi moolnii mo e MaaЙ—a e jurriiya makko on immorde seytaane raЙ—aaЙ—o on"
  3,37,"Joomi makko JaЙ“irani mo jaЙ“annde moЖҙЖҙere,O Neiri mo needi moЖҙЖҙundi,O Halfini mo Jakariya.Tuma kala Jakariya naati e hoore makko ka Mihraab,o tawda mo e arsike,o wi'a:Hey, Mariyam hol no heЙ“irЙ—aa Й—um?O jaaboo:ЖҠum ko ka Alla iwri.Pellet,no Arsika on O Muuyi ko aldaa e hasboore"
  3,38,"Ko ton Jakariraa'u noddi Jooma mun o maaki: \"Joomi am, YeЙ—am immorde ka MaaЙ—a, jurriiya laaЙ“uЙ—o, pellet, An ko A Nanoowo noddaandu"
  3,39,"Malaa'ika en noddi mo hawri himo darii juuugol ka ganngunal, wonde: \"Alla No Wewlinire Yahyaa, goonginЙ—o Konngol iwrungol ka Alla: koohoojo, e reenaaЙ—o [e tuuyo], e Annabaajo jeyaaЙ—o e moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e\" @Corrected"
  3,40,"O maaki: \"Joomi an, hol no Й“iЙ—Й—o laatorЕӢta lam, gomЙ—ii mi nawyii, debbo am on ko damaro?\" O Daali: \"Ko wano non Alla WaЙ—irta ko O Muuyi [waЙ—de]"
  3,41,"O maaki: \"Joomi, WaЙ—anam maande\". O Daali: \"Maande maa nden, ko nde a yeewtidataa e yimЙ“e Й“en Й“alЙ—e tati si wanaa e joopagol. JaЕӢtoЙ—aa Joomi maaЙ—a ko heewi: subbunhino-Й—aa kiiki e bimmbi"
  3,42,"Tuma nde Malaa'ika en wi'unoo: \"Hey Maryama, pellet Alla SuЙ“ike ma, O LaЙ“Й“inii ma [O SuЙ“ii] e rewЙ“e winndere nden"
  3,43,"Hey Maryam, toЖҙЖҙinano Joomi maa, sujjaa ruЖҙЖҙidaa e ruЖҙЖҙooЙ“e Й“en"
  3,44,"ЖҠum Й—oo, ko jeyaaЙ—um e kumpite wirniiЙ—e, MeЙ—en Wahayina Й—e e maaЙ—a. A tawanooka e maЙ“Й“e nde Й“e weddotonoo kuЙ—i maЙ“Й“e Й—in: ko hommbo e maЙ“Й“e ne'ata Maryama; a tawanooka e maЙ“Й“e kadi nde Й“e wennjaynoo"
  3,45,"Nde Malaa'ika en wi'unoo: \"Hey Maryama, Alla no Wewlinire Konngol immorde e Maako: Innde makko, ko meema-sella, Iisaa geЙ—al Maryama, koohoojo aduna e laakara, jeyaaЙ—a e Й“aЙ—tinaaЙ“e [ka Alla]"
  3,46,"Himo yeewtida e yimЙ“e Й“en ka woofordu=tiggu e ka sagatalaaku, ko o jeyaaЙ—o e moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e Й“en"
  3,47,"O wi'i: \"Joomi am, hol no Й“iЙ—Й—o laatoraЕӢta lam, Й“anndiЕӢke meemaali lam?\". O Daali: \"Ko wano non. Alla no Taga ko O Muuyi. Si O Г‘aawii fiyaake, O Daalanay mo [tun]: \"Laato! o laatoo"
  3,48,Himo Anndina mo Deftere nden e Г‘eeГұal ngal e Tawreeta e Linnjiila
  3,49,"E NulaaЙ—o faade e Й“iЙ“Й“e Israa'iila en, wonnde: \"GomЙ—ii mi addanii on maande immorde ka Joomi mon. Wonnde miЙ—o tagana on immorde e loopal ko wa'i wa sonndu, mi wutta e muuЙ—um woЕӢtira sonndu e DuЕӢayee Alla. Mi wumtina bunЙ—o, mi sellina baadaaЙ—o, mi wuurnitira maayЙ“e e duЕӢayee Alla. Mi humpita on ko Гұaamoton e ko maroton ka cuuЙ—i mon. Pellet, hino e Й—um, maande wonanannde on si on laatike gomЙ—imЙ“e"
  3,50,"e goonginЙ—o ko woni yeeso am immorde e Tawreeta, e no mi dagininirana on yoga e ko harmannoo on, mi addanii on maande immorde ka Joomi mon. Hulee Alla Й—oftoЙ—on lam"
  3,51,"Pellet, ko Alla Woni Joomi am e Joomi mon, rewee Mo. Ko Й—um woni laawol focciingol"
  3,52,"Tuma nde Iisaa so'unoo keeferaaku ngun e maЙ“Й“e, o maaki: \"Ko hommbo wallata lam e [diina] Alla [kan]?\". HawaaruyaЕӢko en wi'i: \"Menen ko men wallooЙ“e [e diina] Alla [kan], men gomЙ—inii Alla, seedo wonnde ko men jebbiiliiЙ“e"
  3,53,"Joomi amen, men gomЙ—inii ko JipinЙ—aa Kon, men jokkii NulaaЙ—o on, Winndu men e seediiЙ“e Й“en"
  3,54,ЖҒe fewji Alla Kadi Fewji. Ko Alla ЖҒuri MoЖҙЖҙude e fewjooЙ“e Й“en
  3,55,"Nde Alla Daalunoo: \"Hey Iisaa, Min ko mi Hunnoowo ma e ЖҒamtoowo ma faade ka Am, e LaЙ“Й“inoowo ma immorde e Й“en yedduЙ“e, e WaЙ—a Й“en jokkuЙ“e ma e hoore Й“en yedduЙ“e haa Г‘alnde Darngal. Refti ko faade ka Am woni ruttorde mon, Mi Г‘aawa hakkunde mon ko luutondirayno-Й—on e muuЙ—um"
  3,56,"Ammaa Й“en yedduЙ“e, Mi Lepta Й“en Й—on lepte muusuЙ—e ka aduna e ka laakara, alanaaЙ“e faabotooЙ“e"
  3,57,"Ammaa Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“e golli golle-moЖҙЖҙe, O Hunnanay Й“e mbarjaari maЙ“Й“e ndin. Alla YiЙ—aa tooГұooЙ“e Й“en"
  3,58,"ЖҠum Й—oo, MeЙ—en Janngana maa Й—um, immorde e Aayeeje e JaЕӢtoore Г‘eГұГұaannde"
  3,59,"Pellet, sifa Iisaa ka Alla, ko sifa Aadama; O Tagii mo immorde e mbummbuldi, refti O Daalani mo: \"Laato!\" o laatii"
  3,60,"Goonga kan ko ko immori ko Joomi maa, wata a laatodu e Й“en sikkitiiЙ“e"
  3,61,"Kala wennjuЙ—o ma fii makko Й“aawo kon ko ar e maa e ganndal, maaku: \"Aree nodden Й“iЙ—Й“e amen e Й“iЙ—Й“e mo'on, e rewЙ“e amen e rewЙ“e mo'on, e ko'e amen e ko'e mo'on, refti ГұaagoЙ—en waЙ—en kuddi Alla ndin e hoore fenooЙ“e Й“en"
  3,62,"Pellet Й—um Й—oo, ko Й—um woni fillayee goonga. Alaa reweteeЙ—o si wanaa Alla, pellet, Alla ko KaЕӢko Woni FooluЙ—o Г‘eeГұuЙ—o"
  3,63,"Si Й“e huccitii, pellet Alla ko AnnduЙ—o bonnooЙ“e Й“en"
  3,64,"Maaku: \"Hey yimЙ“e Defte, aree faade e konngol fotayngol hakkunde amen e mo'on : wonnde en rewataa si wanaa Alla, en kafidataa Mo e huunde, wata yoga e me'en jogito yoga joomiraaЙ“e ko woori Alla\". Si Й“e huccitii, wi'ee: \"Seeditee wonnde menen ko men jebbiliiЙ“e"
  3,65,"Hey yimЙ“e Defte, ko wennjaЕӢton fii Ibraahiima, Tawreeta e Linnjiila Jippinaaka si wanaa Й“aawo makko : e on haqqiltaa"
  3,66,"Hey ko onon Й“ee, on wennjii kon ko anndal woodani on e mu'un, ko wennjaЕӢton ko anndal alanaa on e mu'un? Alla no Anndi onon on anndaa"
  3,67,"Ibraahiima laatanooki AlyahuudiЕӢke wanaa Annasaaraajo, si ko woni, o laatinoke ooГұiiЙ—o [e kala diina] jebbilaniiЙ—o [Diina Lislaamu], o laatanooki jeyaaЙ—o e shirkooЙ“e Й“en"
  3,68,"Pellet, ko Й“uri hanndude e Ibraahiima e yimЙ“e Й“en : ko Й“en jokkuЙ“e mo, e oo Annabiijo, e Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e. Alla ko GiЙ—o gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en"
  3,69,"Fedde goo e yimЙ“e Defte Й“en yelike nde Й“e majjina on, Й“e majjiЕӢtaa si wanaa ko'e maЙ“Й“e Й—en Й“e so'aa anndude"
  3,70,"Hey mon yimЙ“e Defte, e ko yeddaЕӢton Aayeeje Alla ЖҠen hara onon ko on seediiЙ“e"
  3,71,"Hey mon yimЙ“e Defte, e ko jillaЕӢton goonga kan e meh-re nden hiЙ—on suuЙ—a goonga kan hara onon hiЙ—on anndi"
  3,72,"Fedde goo jeyaande e yimЙ“e Defte Й“en wi'i: \"GomЙ—inee ko jippinaa kon e Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e ka arannde Гұallal, yeddon ka sakkitoode mayre, bela jo'o, Й“e ruttoo"
  3,73,"Wata on gomЙ—in si wanaa on jokkuЙ—o diina mon kan\". Maaku: \"Pellet, ko Peewal Alla ngal woni Peewal\". [Ko kulil fii ] wata goЙ—Й—o goo okke sugu ko okkaЙ—on kon maa Й“e wennjiroya on Й—um ko Joomi mon. Maaku: \"Pellet Й“ural ngal ko e Junngo Alla woni, Himo YeЙ—a ngal on Mo O Muuyi\". Alla ko yaajuЙ—o [Й“ural] AnnduЙ—o"
  3,74,Himo Hertinana Yurmeende Makko nden on Mo O muuyi. Alla ko Jom ЖҒural Mawngal
  3,75,"No e yimЙ“e Defte Й“en, on mo halfiЕӢtaa jawdi wonayndi KINTAAR, on jonnite ndi; hino e maЙ“Й“e kadi, on mo halfiЕӢtaa \"diinaaru\", on jonnitataa ma ndu si wanaa a darani mo daЕӢkaranni-Й—aa. ЖҠum non, ko tawde kamЙ“e Й“e wi'i: \"Laatanaaki men e humammbinneeЙ“e Й“en laawol\"; hiЙ“e taЖҙa penaale huma e Alla hara kamЙ“e hiЙ“e anndi"
  3,76,"Aa'a, kala hunnuЙ—o ahadi mu'un o huli, pellet, Alla no YiЙ—i hulooЙ“e Mo Й“en"
  3,77,"ЖҒen soktitorayЙ“e ahadi Alla ndin e goondooje maЙ“Й“e coggeloy famЙ—ukoy, Й“en Й—on, geЙ“al alaa Й“e ka laakara, Alla yeewtidataa e maЙ“Й“e, O Ndaaroytaa Й“e Г‘lande Darngal, O LaЙ“Й“iЕӢtaa Й“e, no woodani Й“e lepte muusuЙ—e"
  3,78,"No e maЙ“Й“e fedde : hiЙ“e ooГұira Й—emЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en e Deftere nden no sikkiron Й—um ko jeyaaЙ—um e Deftere nden, Й—um le jeyaaka e Deftere nden; hiЙ“e wi'a : \"ЖҠum ko ko iwri ka Alla\", Й—um le wanaa ka Alla iwri; hiЙ“e takka penaale hoore Alla hara kamЙ“e hiЙ“e anndi"
  3,79,"Laatanaaki Й“anndiЕӢke nde Alla Okkata mo Deftere e fahmu e Annabaaku, refti o wi'ana yimЙ“e Й“en: \"Laatee jeyaaЙ“e am ko woori Alla\", si ko woni: \"Laatoree tutiiЙ“e-e-gannde-diina, ko laatinoЙ—on hiЙ—on janngina Deftere nden e ko laatiЙ—on hiЙ—on jannga\" @Corrected"
  3,80,Wanaa nde o yamirta on jogitorgol Malaa'ika en e AnnabaaЙ“e Й“en reweteeЙ“e. E o yamiray on keeferaaku Й“aawo nde wonЙ—on julЙ“e
  3,81,"Tuma nde Alla Жҙettunoo ahadi e AnnabaaЙ“e Й“en : \"Si Mi Addanii on Deftere e fahmu, refti NulaaЙ—o ari e mo'on goonginЙ—o kon ko jogiЙ—on, ma on gomЙ—in mo wallitoЙ—on mo\". O Daali: \"E on qirritike Й—um, on Жҙettii e hoore mun ahadi?\". ЖҒe wi'i: \"Men qirritike\". O Daali: \"Seeditee, MiЙ—o wondi e mo'on ka seeditiiЙ“e"
  3,82,"On huccituЙ—o Й“aawo Й—um, ko Й“en woni faasiqiiЙ“e Й“en"
  3,83,"E ko woori Diina Alla kan Й“e Й—aЙ“Й“ata? Hino woodani Mo jebbilaare Й“en wonЙ“e ka kammuuli e ka leydi, Й—oftaare maa waawneede, ko faade ka Makko Й“e ruttotoo"
  3,84,"Maaku: \"Men gomЙ—inii Alla e ko jippinaa dow amen e ko jippinaa dow Ibrahiima e Isma'iila e Ishaaqa e Yaaquuba e TaaniraaЙ“e Й“en e ko Muusaa e Iisaa okkaa e AnnabaaЙ“e Й“en immorde ka Joomi maЙ“Й“e. Men serndataa hakkunde gooto e maЙ“Й“e, Menen wonannde Mo ko men jebbiliiЙ“e"
  3,85,"Kala Й—aЙ“Й“uЙ—o ko woori Lislaamu on Diina, o jaЙ“aЕӢtaake Й—um, on Й—on ka laakara, ko o jeyaaЙ—o e hayruЙ“e Й“en"
  3,86,"Hol no Alla Fewnirta yimЙ“e yedduЙ“e Й“aawo gomЙ—inal maЙ“Й“e Й“e seedii wonnde NulaaЙ—o on ko goonga, Й“anngannduyeeji Й—in arii Й“e? Alla Fewnataa yimЙ“e tooГұooЙ“e Й“en"
  3,87,"ЖҒen Й—on, joЙ“di maЙ“Й“e ndin, ko no fawii Й“e kuddi Alla ndin e Malaa'ika en e yimЙ“e Й“en Й“e denndaangal"
  3,88,"Ko Й“e luttooЙ“e e magge. ЖҒe hayfinaЕӢtaake lepte Й—en, Й“e wonaali nennanaЕӢteeЙ“e"
  3,89,"Si wanaa Й“en tuubuЙ“e Й“aawo Й—um Й“e moЖҙЖҙini. Pellet, Alla ko YaafotooЙ—o YurmeteeЙ—o"
  3,90,"Pellet, Й“en yedduЙ“e Й“aawo gomЙ—inal maЙ“Й“e, refti Й“e Й“eydorii keeferaaku, tuubugol maЙ“Й“e jaЙ“etaake; ko Й“en Й—on woni majjuЙ“e Й“en"
  3,91,"Pellet, Й“en yedduЙ“e Й“e maayi ko Й“e heererЙ“e, gooto e maЙ“Й“e jaЙ“aЕӢtaake, leydi ndin tew kaЕӢЕӢe; hay si o soktorii Й—um. ЖҒen Й—on, no woodani Й“e lepte muusuЙ—e, Й“e alaa wallooЙ“e"
  3,92,"On heЙ“ataa moЖҙЖҙere nden haa wiЕӢtoЙ—on e ko Й“uruЙ—on yiЙ—ude kon. Kala woo ko wiЕӢtiЙ—on, pellet Alla no Anndi Й—um"